title: Top O' The MornTrend 3/17: Chris Cuomo, Brittney Griner, Kanye West, Dolly Parton, Jumanji, St. Patty's Day
itunes:title: Top O' The MornTrend 3/17: Chris Cuomo, Brittney Griner, Kanye West, Dolly Parton, Jumanji, St. Patty's Day
description:
In this edition of Top O' The MornTrend, Jack and Miles discuss Chris Cuomo suing CNN, Brittney Griner's Russian detention getting extended until May, Kanye getting suspended from Instagram, the Rock and Roll Hall of Fame refusing to pull Dolly Parton from their ballot (against her wishes), the 'Jumanji' theme park ride, and St. Patty's Day horror stories!

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
